race.comment: HANDLE BARS DOWN (4) stuck on well last time to finish one length back in second (26.46) at this track in a Restricted WIN over 461m. Top prospect. THROW HANDS (1) is suited by the inside draw. Latest effort finished 6th in a Restricted WIN on October 2 over 340m at this track behind Disfunctional beaten 4.5 lengths (20.01). Can hit the frame with the right run. FIRMLY FIXED (2) turned in a moderate run last time when eighth at Launceston over 278m behind Rusty Ploughman (16.98) in a Other. Was in the money the start prior. A big run wouldn't surprise. OVER IS OVER (6) was out of the money here last time out but can bounce back.
